@item -b STYLE
@itemx --bubble STYLE
@itemx --balloon STYLE
@opindex @option{-b}
@opindex @option{--bubble}
@opindex @option{--balloon}
Specify the balloon style that should used, this can either be a file name or a
balloon name printed by @option{ponysay -B}. This option can be used multiple
